The paper also discusses the use of synthetic data and 3D models, which are common in computer graphics and robotics, hence cs.GR and cs.RO are also possible sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves training a neural network, which is a common topic in machine learning and deep learning, hence cs.LG is also a possible sub-category.
